<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.273729>
    dc:description "FIGURES 11 - 13. 11. Zanysson gemmatus sp. nov., female (holotype). Metanotum and scutellum in posterior view. 12. Zanysson argentinus, female. Metanotum and scutellum in posterior view. 13. Zanysson gemmatus sp. nov., male (paratype). Dorsal and posterior face of propodeum." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/273729/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.273726>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 4. Zanysson gemmatus sp. nov., female (holotype) and male (paratype). 1. Body in lateral view, female. 2. Head and thorax in lateral view, female. 3. Head and thorax in posterolateral view, male. 4. Head and thorax in oblique dorsolateral view, male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/273726/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.273727>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 7. Zanysson gemmatus sp. nov., female (holotype) and male (paratype). 5. Body in dorsal view, female. 6. Head in frontal view, female. 7. Head in frontal view, male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/273727/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.273728>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8 – 10. Zanysson gemmatus sp. nov., female (holotype) and male (paratype). 8. Head and thorax in dorsal view, female. 9. Abdomen in posterodorsal view, female. 10. Abdomen in posterodorsal view, male." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/273728/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

